metadata.name: KookyKats #1
metadata.description: Kooky Kats is a community-focused project with real-world application. Each adopted Kat becomes part of our family, gains access to exclusive content and unlocks early access to our mobile game, World of Kats. To those who roam the alleys, and for those who wander the streets, Kooky Kats is a community and a home for everyone.
